 `ErrorsInnerPluginsTest` again to let `JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(...)` return normally when a graphical display is available.\n\nUpdated:\n\n- `tests/src/com.diffplug.durian/durian-core/1.2.0/src/test/java/com_diffplug_durian/durian_core/ErrorsInnerPluginsTest.java`\n\nKey changes:\n\n- Removed forced `java.awt.headless=true`, which made `showMessageDialog.invoke(...)` throw and likely prevented line coverage for `Errors.java:450`.\n- Added a repeating Swing `Timer` that disposes any showing windows, so the dialog can open and close automatically without hanging.\n- Kept `SwingUtilities.invokeAndWait(...)` to flush the queued `invokeLater` runnable from `defaultDialog(...)`.\n- Preserved fallback behavior so the test still passes in headless environments, while allowing normal-return coverage of the remaining call site when a display is available.\n\nPer instruction, I did not compile or run tests.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e16fa176372072f0169f4d0df4b68819286fd3776627dc654\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1159, "output": 321, "cacheRead": 57856, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 59336, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777651931845, "responseId": "resp_0e16fa176372072f0169f4d0dc6a348192afe5f29481ac1c57"}, "toolResults": []}
